comment_text:
1. There is not a single actual photograph or video of blue-marble earth (ALL CGI);
2. there are no "orbiting" satellites (only hanging on balloons & in circling aircraft);
3. There were no moon landings (see
Stanley Kubrick & Bart Sibrel);
4. There is no "orbiting" ISS (there IS a
"training replica" in a swimming pool & we see the tiny escaping bubbles in supposed space walks).
5. There is no space, no spherical planets ("wandering stars") or stars - they are all luminary objects & the rest is pure, speculative fantasy;
6. NASA/Disney/Google Earth is a CIA psy-op against the public "for their own good."
No curvature, no globe. No globe, no spin.
The universe rotates above a flat, stationary plane. We actually ARE the center of our observable universe.
